        <p>
          The Association of Software Engineering at NSBM, formerly known as the
          Student Circle of Software Engineering, was established in February
          2024 under the guidance of the Department of Software Engineering and
          Information Systems. The association was formed to foster a
          collaborative environment where students following a discipline in
          Software Engineering could enhance their skills, share knowledge, and
          engage in various activities that complement their academic pursuits.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-image">
